{
  "texts": [
    "In their study to predict molecular properties, Jiang et al.",
    "showed that GNN was better than other property prediction methods (Jiang et al., 2021).",
    "According to recent research, the characteristics of compounds may be reliably predicted using a particular GNN named Chemi-Net (Liu et al., 2019).",
    "While GNNs are among the most cutting-edge approaches to molecular DL setup, they have flaws.",
    "For example, GNNs have unique challenges, such as over-smoothing."
  ]
}